{
  "texts": [
    "However, Generative AI has rapidly precipitated a greater mix of natural language and abstract code (Yang et al. 2024).",
    "The purely procedural and mechanical parts of the code have been automated, and code can be generated with natural language prompts.",
    "In a certain way, computer coding and mathematics have always been specialized-if unnaturalwriting practices by virtue of their extreme formality.",
    "But now natural language plays a closer role in both.",
    "Indeed, Generative AI's prompt engineering is a form of natural language programming."
  ]
}